attr.attrdef: Type of trail. Greenway, Greenway Entrance, Dirtway, Dirtway Entrance, etc.
Trail surface material. Concrete, Asphalt, Packed Gravel, etc.
Provides information about each greenway segment. As an example, a segment can be a reach of greenway between two streets which define a specific section of greenway.
Length of greenway segment in feet
This defines the time when a segment of greenway is captured via GPS, this typically relates to the time of construction completion and the greenway is available for public use.
Distance of greenway segment calculated in US miles
